# Lint/type-check tooling for the CI "lint" job.
# Compiled to lint.txt with hashes via: make pip-compile
#
# The runtime deps (mcp, pydantic) are included so mypy --strict can resolve
# the FastMCP and pydantic types rather than treating them as untyped.
# ruff/black are pinned to the exact versions the CI lint job uses so the
# check stays deterministic across uv recompiles.
